Create a clear job description with these sections:
1. Role summary
2. Key responsibilities
3. Required qualifications
4. Preferred qualifications
5. Success profile
6. Interview focus areas
7. Inclusive closing note
Keep the writing concrete, neutral, and candidate-friendly.

